{"tid":1318951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得之前有臺灣團體建議臺灣政府限制黑警入境？","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:28.000Z","uid":125026,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"513337582bf702b9334dfcf40c0f31f1272ad0a7","tid":1318951,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得一個月前，有個post係話臺灣公民團體呼籲立法院、行政院，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將黑警、公務員視作中國人，甚至係黨政軍人員處理</span></strong>，換言之，黑警同公務員以後去臺灣就會好Ｑ麻煩，當時陸委會嘅回應係，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「將評估香港情勢，作為是否調整香港政策的依據」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n事件已經過咗一個月，香港情勢變成點我諗大家都好清楚，唔知我地可唔可以拎返呢件事出黎講，等黑警初嚐被制裁嘅滋味呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗱，臺灣嘅公民團體已經幫我地開咗個頭，寫咗咁大篇聲明，我覺得我地應該好好利用，我諗以港臺咁友好嘅關係，應該有得搞，大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原Post：《制裁開波！台灣團體要求政府立法 管制香港公務員入境》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202268/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202268/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"170130b34c2597cdaabcfb032909297d53f96e92","tid":1318951,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6be785eeef974e222d47ea57c88709c3d5ab5c","tid":1318951,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f691b6620cb917840ba29d199ca888efc8a4d056","tid":1318951,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講　</code>"},{"pid":"715522232a07a8a64ac10ca905699f2c8fe7308c","tid":1318951,"uid":125026,"like":0,"disl